    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and remains in impressive condition both inside and out. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish with only the minor, expected road wear consistent with careful ownership. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean, smoke-free, and all electronic features\u2014from the responsive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is rock-solid; it boasts a documented history of regular synthetic oil changes and a recent comprehensive brake service, ensuring a smooth, quiet, and reliable driving experience. It sits on a set of premium tires with significant tread remaining. This is a dependable, well-sorted example that balances aesthetic appeal with mechanical integrity, ready for its next owner to drive away with total confidence.",
      "price": 34800.0,
